{"tid":1033163,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本擬收支付寶「QR Code」專利使用費　《環球時報》：手機技術是中国人的","createTime":"2019-02-23T02:15:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-27T16:20:47.000Z","uid":184679,"like":78,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"9a7005ffa88ee6d7c72f19b87b6ecab7b73d8378","tid":1033163,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T02:15:53.000Z","msg":"中國近年來推動「無現金交易」，使用普及率最高的「支付寶」也在2018年大肆侵略日本，但該程式使用的「QR Code」是日本人發明，的現在日方考慮對此申請專利，未來向使用此服務的中國人每人收取1分人民幣（約台幣4.57分）的費用。<br />\n<br />\n根據《環球網》報導，「QR Code」是日本「電裝公司（Denso）」在1994年的新創發明，目前是子公司DENSO WAVE的業務。而當年電裝公司並沒有想要獨佔技術，反倒為了讓「QR Code」普及率提高，無償提供「QR Code」的製作程式，一方面販賣掃碼設備，許多日本便利商店、超級市場開始使用這項技術，但並未推廣到其他國家。<br />\n<br />\n《環球網》指出，中國人首先發現「QR Code」蘊含的無限商機，意銳新創公司的創始人王越在2001年學到了日本的「QR Code」技術，在沒得到重用的情況下回到中國創業，2003年將此技術申請中國專利，報導提到，發明「QR Code」的日本此時反而喪失競爭力。<br />\n<br />\n有鑑於中客在日本使用支付寶的頻率逐漸提高，有意申請專利，DENSO WAVE執行董事田路勝彥表示，「經常有人跟我說一個QR Code收10分錢也好」，但《環球網》批評，中國「凌空網」創始人徐蔚已在2011年成功獲得美國、歐洲與日本的「QR Code」技術專利，日方的想法無疑屬於無稽之談。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2707316\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2707316&d=gMg1FBwAZA1XbJy1Uvmn1P7c%2B9HD3JYLAdxAiSxEDXo%3D&h=0ef5787f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2707316&h=39c46209\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2707316</a>"},{"pid":"35276465c2bd4c45e3fd7d67194895720ea28a76","tid":1033163,"uid":121146,"like":81,"dislike":2,"score":79,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T02:20:42.000Z","msg":"中國人最叻係搶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d20358d1be18cbe65cd047a7031d1559a075cb8","tid":1033163,"uid":41389,"like":19,"dislike":3,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"35276465c2bd4c45e3fd7d67194895720ea28a76","tid":1033163,"uid":121146,"like":81,"dislike":2,"score":79,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T02:20:42.000Z","msg":"中國人最叻係搶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T02:21:08.000Z","msg":"一不靠。。 二不靠。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b2da80db3a42f9ad7a2499e5525376c7eb9406a","tid":1033163,"uid":47259,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T02:41:58.000Z","msg":"環球膠報呢隻豬隊友臨美中貿易談判之前仲跳出嚟派膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f2fc45a11ffd7c841d00301cbd4ee6a514e9cf7","tid":1033163,"uid":57376,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T02:46:02.000Z","msg":"支那人最鍾意用嘅野偏偏來自最憎嘅小日本鬼子<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全部都係漢奸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee05c73d959ea3c9a1d2a7d1031f4dcdb5e9e597","tid":1033163,"uid":196994,"like":1,"dislike":25,"score":-24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T02:49:46.000Z","msg":"中國當年本海國圖治喺本地得唔到重用流入日本 帶來日本維新運動的改變成為當時世界強國 中國需要向日本收取專利費用 商業角度上 你沒獨佔專利  對家發現商機進一步發展技術都無可厚非"},{"pid":"b81951691445dbdad44b0f6f6a0965494c0a31b1","tid":1033163,"uid":25108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T02:50:20.000Z","msg":"全球都用緊先黎申請專利有得咁架咩"},{"pid":"52b12c1334a02d6ddf0b791b0cf16eb5f30e2b25","tid":1033163,"uid":213597,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T02:50:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bb4e934c17e9b1f139308699bc40c24d130105c4","tid":1033163,"uid":29916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b81951691445dbdad44b0f6f6a0965494c0a31b1","tid":1033163,"uid":25108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T02:50:20.000Z","msg":"全球都用緊先黎申請專利有得咁架咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T02:55:27.000Z","m