2c80380e5ef98e0f857b86626524edb6f9","tid":1033163,"uid":29916,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"0421f8bf96c61f3109280f5565a1ebb344de9c38","tid":1033163,"uid":155737,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T03:33:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.qrcode.com/en/patent.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.qrcode.com%2Fen%2Fpatent.html&d=gMg1FBwAZA1XbJy1Uvmn1P7c%2B9HD3JYLAdxAiSxEDXo%3D&h=3fd68c24\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.qrcode.com/en/patent.html</a><br />\nDenso唔係有哂patent喇咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n嗰件支那人乜水嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T10:14:37.000Z","msg":"好多已經到期"},{"pid":"eb48368f6d615d08e3ba70b73e5fe53751fe7ca9","tid":1033163,"uid":41308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d5bb02c80380e5ef98e0f857b86626524edb6f9","tid":1033163,"uid":29916,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"0421f8bf96c61f3109280f5565a1ebb344de9c38","tid":1033163,"uid":155737,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T03:33:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.qrcode.com/en/patent.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.qrcode.com%2Fen%2Fpatent.html&d=gMg1FBwAZA1XbJy1Uvmn1P7c%2B9HD3JYLAdxAiSxEDXo%3D&h=3fd68c24\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.qrcode.com/en/patent.html</a><br />\nDenso唔係有哂patent喇咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n嗰件支那人乜水嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T10:14:37.000Z","msg":"好多已經到期"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T03:21:42.000Z","msg":"過左期。第二間公司都唔可以申請專利。問題在於，支那條友話支那為QR code申請左專利。<br />\n<br />\n我好想Denso wave收支那寶錢，但專利過左期就收唔到"},{"pid":"309d0f7161095fddc8726d7fe5fe540182bf3458","tid":1033163,"uid":41317,"like":2,"dislike":15,"score":-13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T03:37:07.000Z","msg":"當初日本仔自己opensource, 剩係靠device賺錢<br />\n見人用起左就話想做專利收返錢<br />\n又唔諗下冇大陸qrcode一定做唔起<br />\n當初日本qrcode做唔起就係因為啲epayment選擇用更快嘅nfc<br />\n係大陸先on99走去用qrcode<br />\n<br />\n如果掉返轉係大陸發明qrcode, 日本做起, 然後大陸想收返錢<br />\n你地咪一樣屌大陸輸打贏要"},{"pid":"a8e434fa8dc0b32b1ee01bfb550fa1c523f66545","tid":1033163,"uid":130695,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T03:55:46.000Z","msg":"大陸閪文化 偷呃擄騙搶<br />\n口技世界第一 東莞三十六式<br />\n問做雞 誰與爭峰<br />\n論外交 有睇周星馳都知啦 嘴炮呀！<br />\n屋企煮飯引致霧霾 仲可以防激光<br />\n有毒氣體對人體無害<br />\n除左騙子咩都假<br />\n紙皮豬肉包，頭髮豉油，地溝油，黑心蛋，豬瘟腸<br />\n知唔知點解有大頭奶粉呀！<br />\n因為大陸閪普遍智商低下<br />\n而腦一般同頭既呎吋成正比<br />\n點知食完都係朦撚一堆！<br />\n仲要有班傻閪唔識欣賞<br />\n你估呢啲国家特產邊度都食到咩<br />\n走黎食人地既奶 啪人地既針 拆人家庭搶人間屋<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n渣住本垃圾国護照就屌人要人認中国人<br />\n又要仆住搶其他國家護照<br />\n死磨爛磨 面皮無限厚 到班畜生拎到<br />\n即時又扮愛国 話做中国狗最好<br />\n要其他人繼續做隻中国狗要愛国<br />\n所以話中国支那賤畜蝗蟲真係幾撚恐怖<br />\n無人格無人性唯利是圖<br />\n玩個人崇拜 當個小熊維尼係皇帝<br />\n做哂太監宮女爭住奶<br />\n丫，我唔記得左<br />\n中国係最無骨氣既地方，打亂種<br />\n滿漢明清乜撚族都有<br />\n不過呢 都係中国狗，何必分那麼細<br />\n<br />\n一句 中国又贏呀！"},{"pid":"3bc72cd57089774aca66ccf01cdbe3d6c8d03272","tid":1033163,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T04:42:56.000Z","msg":"即係QR Code現階段係唔存在專利？"},{"pid":"458301cbc225f8a63e70d08a9844ce0975920ea6","tid":1033163,"uid":41308,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"309d0f7161095fddc8726d7fe5fe540182bf3458","tid":1033163,"uid":41317,"like":2,"dislike":15,"score":-13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T03:37:07.000Z","msg":"當初日本仔自己opensource, 剩係靠device賺錢<br />\n見人用起左就話想做專利收返錢<br />\n又唔諗下冇大陸qrcode一定做唔起<br />\n當初日本qrcode做唔起就係因為啲epayment選擇用更快嘅nfc<br />\n係大陸先on99走去用qrcode<br />\n<br />\n如果掉返轉係大陸發明qrcode, 日本做起, 然後大陸想收返錢<br />\n你地咪一樣屌大陸輸打贏要"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T04:51:22.000Z","msg":"根本payment 應該用更安全既NFC<br />\n<br />\n同埋QR code無大陸樣可以流行"},{"pid":"a2c14e8eeaf5fe91008da7adbcf0a0c588160b3e","tid":1033163,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee05c73d959ea3c9a1d2a7d1031f4dcdb5e9e597","tid":10331